1801:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         user board environment or can be calculated using ADC measurement
1802:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and ADC helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CALC_VREFANALOG_VOLTAGE().
