3593:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC continuous conversion mode on ADC group regular.
3594:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Description of ADC continuous conversion mode:
3595:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - single mode: one conversion per trigger
3596:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - continuous mode: after the first trigger, following
3597:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           conversions launched successively automatically.
3598:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   It is not possible to enable both ADC group regular
3599:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         continuous mode and sequencer discontinuous mode.
3600:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
3601:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
3602:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled.
3603:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CFGR1    CONT           LL_ADC_REG_SetContinuousMode
3604:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
3605:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  Continuous This parameter can be one of the following values:
3606:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_CONV_SINGLE
3607:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_CONV_CONTINUOUS
3608:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @retval None
3609:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
3610:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** __STATIC_INLINE void LL_ADC_REG_SetContinuousMode(ADC_TypeDef *ADCx, uint32_t Continuous)
