3654:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled.
3655:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CFGR1    DMAEN          LL_ADC_REG_SetDMATransfer\n
3656:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         CFGR1    DMACFG         LL_ADC_REG_SetDMATransfer
