3660:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_DMA_TRANSFER_LIMITED
3661:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_DMA_TRANSFER_UNLIMITED
