3748:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
3749:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set sampling time of the selected ADC channel
3750:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Unit: ADC clock cycles.
